CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 10, 1956, pg. 26 reads: "Who Will Be "Miss WILY"? you pick the winner...Bernice Catherine Kuzma, Munhall, Announcement of the winner and the coronation of "Miss WILY" will take place at Warners Cinerama, 336 Fifth Ave., Tuesday Evening, November 27th."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Bernice Catherine Kuzma wearing a light colored short sleeve blouse and dark tweed skirt, posed in interior with light colored walls for "Miss WILY" contest
